{"type": "article", "id": 5900, "title": "巴黎“坏男孩”和施华洛世奇联手推出一堆石头", "description": "Swarovski 和 Jean-Paul Gaultier 联手推出“石头”饰品。", "date": "2015-02-05T08:04:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 6781, "name": "Swarovski"}, {"id": 6782, "name": "Jean-Paul Gaultier"}, {"id": 6783, "name": "饰品"}], "category": 18, "author": 50193, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604223422SKzTomJ6Uq3sn0wh.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jean-paul-gaultier-unveils-jewelry-768598\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><span class=\"s1\">据</span> Pret-A-Reporter </a><span class=\"s1\"><a href=\"http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jean-paul-gaultier-unveils-jewelry-768598\" target=\"_blank\">报道</a>，</span>Jean-Paul Gaultier <span class=\"s1\">在此次巴黎高定秀场上首次展示了自己品牌和施华洛世奇的合作系列，并将该系列命名为</span> “Kaput”<span class=\"s1\">。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t据<span class=\"s2\"> Gaultier </span>本人解释，<span class=\"s2\">“Kaput”</span>是德语破碎或不能使用的东西的意思。但是他认为它就是石头本身。你可以用它做任何东西。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606042234205s7ReiaMP3O0GjDQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t图片来自：<a href=\"http://www.style.com/fashion-shows/spring-2015-couture/jean-paul-gaultier\" target=\"_blank\">Style</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\">Gaultier </span>此次设计的珠宝主要为大块的人造水晶和重金属，准确地传达出作者想要表示的石头的天然质感。<span class=\"s2\">Gaultier </span>告诉<span class=\"s2\"> Pret-A-Reporter </span>说：<span class=\"s2\">”</span>每一件都运用到石头不同的面，有些是不反光的，有些是闪光的，有些是透明的，还有些是黑暗的，有点立体主义。<span class=\"s2\">”</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p3\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s2\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604223420ebVutSTf7PkHahpJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s3\">图片来自：<a href=\"http://vogue.globo.com/moda/moda-news/noticia/2015/01/jean-paul-gaultier-assina-linha-de-cristais-para-swarovski.html\" target=\"_blank\">globo </a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s3\">自 </span><span class=\"s4\">1997 </span><span class=\"s3\">年创建高定系列以来</span><span class=\"s4\">, <span style=\"white-space:normal;\">Jean-Paul Gaultier</span> </span><span class=\"s3\">一直将 </span><span class=\"s2\">Swarovski </span><span class=\"s3\">水晶融入到他的设计作品，既有饰品的运用，也有服装的点缀。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s3\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604223421HyISxt8aGV2D1Y7l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p5\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s3\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p6\">\r\n\tJean-Paul Gaultier <span class=\"s5\">和</span><span class=\"s3\"> </span>Swarovski <span class=\"s1\">的</span><span class=\"s1\">合作还没有结束，今年</span> 7 <span class=\"s1\">月还会有更多的珠宝在</span> Swarovski <span class=\"s1\">的指定店铺中展出、售卖。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p6\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://www.fashion-premiere.com/?p=11155&amp;lang=zh-hans\" target=\"_blank\">fashion-premiere</a> <a href=\"http://brand.swarovski.com/Content.Node/ourinitiatives/fashion/parisfashionweek/ss08/jpgaultier/gallery/gaultier11.zh.html#/zh/ourinitiatives/fashion/Collective15\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Swarovski 官网</a></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}